# 🎯 AI Mock Interview Platform

An AI-powered mock interview platform designed to help users practice interviews through text and voice responses with intelligent performance analysis and real-time feedback.

---

## 🚀 Features

✅ Text-Based Interview Questions  
✅ Voice Answer Support (Speech-to-Text)  
✅ AI-Powered Answer Evaluation  
✅ Grammar & Fluency Analysis  
✅ Confidence Scoring System  
✅ Interview History Tracking  
✅ Professional Dashboard UI  
✅ Real-Time Feedback Generation

---

## 🛠 Tech Stack

### Frontend
- HTML5
- CSS3
- JavaScript

### Backend
- Node.js
- Express.js

### AI Engine
- Python
- Flask
- spaCy

### Database
- MySQL
- Local Storage (Development)

---

## 📂 Project Architecture

```txt
Frontend
   ↓
Node.js / Express Backend
   ↓
Flask AI Engine
   ↓
MySQL Database
```

---

## ⚙️ Installation & Setup

### 1. Clone Repository

```bash
git clone https://github.com/YOUR_USERNAME/YOUR_REPOSITORY.git
cd YOUR_REPOSITORY
```

### 2. Install Backend Dependencies

```bash
npm install
```

### 3. Start Node Backend

```bash
npm start
```

### 4. Setup AI Engine

Move to Python service directory:

```bash
cd ai-engine
```

Install dependencies:

```bash
pip install -r requirements.txt
```

Run Flask server:

```bash
python app.py
```

### 5. Launch Frontend

Open:

```txt
index.html
```

or use Live Server extension.

